    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking,</p><p>Add your <strong>carrot & cabbage</strong> <strong>slaw mix</strong> to a bowl with<strong> </strong>the juice of <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lime[s]</strong>, your <strong>mayo </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>lime slaw</strong></p>",
