    {
      "instruction": "<p>Finely dice your<strong> tomato[es] </strong>and cut the <strong>remaining lime[s]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Add the <strong>diced tomato</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>remaining lime zest</strong>, a<strong> </strong>squeeze of<strong> lime juice</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Mix it all together – this is your<strong> tomato lime salsa</strong></p>",
